@@TJvWinHelp.SetWindowPos@Integer@Integer@Integer@Integer@Integer
Description:
Displays the Help window, if it is minimized or in memory, and sets its size and position as specified.

Parameters:
Left: 
Specifies the x-coordinate of the upper-left corner of the window, in screen coordinates.
Top:
Specifies the y-coordinate of the upper-left corner of the window, in screen coordinates.
Width: 
Specifies the window width, in pixels.
Height: integer
Specifies the window height, in pixels.
Visibility: 
Specifies how to show the window. (SW_SHOW, SW_HIDE, ...).

