@@TJvWinHelp.ShowContents
Description:
Displays the topic specified by the Contents option in the [OPTIONS] section of the .HPJ file.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvWinHelp.ShowContextualHelp@TWinControl
Description:
Display the topic identified in the specified control in a popup menu.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvWinHelp.ShowHelp@TWinControl
