----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvWinHelp.ShowHelpOnHelp
Description:
Displays help on how to use Windows Help, if the WINHELP.HLP file is available.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvWinHelp.ShowIndex
Description:
Displays the Index in the Help Topics dialog box.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvWinHelp.ShowKeyword@string
Description:
Displays the topic in the keyword table that matches the specified keyword, if there is an exact match. if there is more than one match, displays the Index with the topics listed in the Topics Found list box.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvWinHelp.ShowPartialKeyWord@string
Description:
Displays the topic in the keyword table that matches the specified keyword, if there is an exact match. if there is more than one match, displays the Index tab.

